languages.text: "Приветствую, Ваша Светлость. Не сочтите за попытку торопить вас, но я надеюсь, что наша сделка еще в силе. Станция испытывает все большие трудности с провизией".

traits.locale_text: "Приветствую, Ваше благородие. Не сочтите за попытку торопить вас, но я надеюсь, что наша сделка еще в силе. Станция испытывает все большие трудности с провизией".

languages.text: "Greetings, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I don't mean to hurry you, but I do hope that our deal is still in place. The station continues to experience increasingly severe shortages of provisions."

languages.text: 「ご機嫌よう、陛下。急かすつもりはないが、私達の契約はまだ有効であることを願っているよ。ステーションではいまだに食料不足が深刻だ」

languages.text: “您好，大人。我不想催您，但我真诚地希望我们之间的协议依然生效。这座星站依然在面临日益严重的物资短缺问题。”

languages.text: «Saludos, {mf|milord|milady}. No pretendo {mf|apresurarle|apresurarla}, pero espero que nuestro acuerdo siga en pie. La estación sigue experimentando cada vez más escasez de provisiones».
languages.original_text: "Greetings, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I don't mean to hurry you, but I do hope that our deal is still in place. The station continues to experience increasingly severe shortages of provisions."

languages.text: « Bonjour, Votre Seigneurie. Loin de moi l'idée de vous presser, mais j'espère que notre accord tient toujours. Les pénuries de nourriture se font de plus en plus graves dans toute la station. »
languages.original_text: "Greetings, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I don't mean to hurry you, but I do hope that our deal is still in place. The station continues to experience increasingly severe shortages of provisions."

languages.text: "Seid gegrüßt, Eure {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft}. Ich will Euch nicht hetzen, aber ich hoffe, unsere Vereinbarung gilt noch. Die Station leidet weiterhin unter extremer Lebensmittelknappheit."

languages.text: "Merhabalar {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri. İki ayağınızı bir pabuca sokmam istemem ama umarım anlaşmamız hâlâ geçerlidir. İstasyondaki erzak sıkıntısı her geçen gün yüzünü daha da gösteriyor."
languages.original_text: "Greetings, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I don't mean to hurry you, but I do hope that our deal is still in place. The station continues to experience increasingly severe shortages of provisions."

traits.locale_text: "Merhabalar {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri. Sizi aceleye getirmek istemem ama umarım anlaşmamız hâlâ geçerlidir. İstasyondaki erzak sıkıntısı giderek artan şiddette yaşanmaya devam ediyor."
